  "original_title": "\u201c\u0da2\u0dba\u0dc3\u0dcf\u0d9c\u0dbb\u201d \u0d85\u0db0\u0dd2\u0d9a\u0dcf\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0dba\u0da7 \u0db4\u0dad\u0dca \u0d9a\u0dbb\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Appoints \u201cJayasagara\u201d authority",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Navy says that the \"Jayasagara\" ship, which was assigned to the Coast Guard Department by the Navy, was recently assigned to the Coast Guard Ship \"Jayasagara\" and joined the Coast Guard Fleet.",
        "Defense Secretary General (Retired) Kamal Gunaratne recently conducted the ceremony at the Trincomalee Naval Thathakangana Premises.",
        "The Navy says that the Navy handed over the CG 61 ship to the Coast Guard Department last January.",
        "The CG 61 ship has performed a special mission for the Navy for 4 decades, and after being handed over to the Coast Guard Department, the Navy says that it was given the name Jayasagara.",
        "The Jayasagara ship commissioned by the authority is 39.8 meters long, 7 meters wide and has a displacement of 313 tons.",
        "Includes a crew of 10 officers and 68 sailors."
      ],
